        <updateDate>2018-08-13T17:30:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Transportation Workforce Modernization Act</strong></p> <p> This bill authorizes the Department of Transportation to make grants to institutions of higher education and other entities to establish curriculum for a transportation worker retraining program for workers displaced by the adoption of automated driving systems.</p> <p>The Government Accountability Office shall study and report on the impact of driverless vehicle adoption on specified sectors of the economy. <br> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
